public class ReasonFlags
extends DERBitString
The ReasonFlags object. 
 ReasonFlags ::= BIT STRING {
      unused                  (0),
      keyCompromise           (1),
      cACompromise            (2),
      affiliationChanged      (3),
      superseded              (4),
      cessationOfOperation    (5),
      certificateHold         (6),
      privilegeWithdrawn      (7),
      aACompromise            (8) }
